# Cross-Platform Line Endings Configuration
# Forces Unix-style line endings (LF) for core text files to prevent issues

# Global default: auto-detect text files and normalize line endings to LF on check-in
* text=auto eol=lf

# Source Code & Configurations (Text)
*.ts text
*.js text
*.json text
*.md text
*.yaml text
*.yml text
*.env* text

# Binary Files (Images & Media)
# Tells Git not to attempt line-ending normalization or diffing for binaries
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
